Protocol Research & Original Implementation
-------------------------------------------
LibrePods by Kavish Devar (@kavishdevar)
https://github.com/kavishdevar/librepods
License: GPL-3.0

The Apple AirPods Protocol (AAP) implementation in this project is based on
the reverse-engineering work done by the LibrePods project.

